   <h3><br> A Random Quotation:</h3> 
   <br> 
   <p> 
    <!--#include virtual="/cgi-bin/rand_text.pl"--></p> 
   <hr size="3"> 
   <h3>The Collection</h3> 
   <p>This page points to a collection of mathematical quotations culled from many sources. You may conduct a keyword search through the quotation database by clicking <a href="http://math.furman.edu/~mwoodard/form.html">here.<img src="http://math.furman.edu/~mwoodard/search.gif" align="center" hspace="1" vspace="1" width="37" height="33"></a><br> <br> <b>Now, By popular demand, you may download the whole collection at once.</b><br> (It's about 243k...83 printed pages or so.) <br> <a href="http://math.furman.edu/~mwoodard/data.html">Follow this link to download the entire collection.</a> </p> 
   <p>Of course, you may also access the quotations "page by page". They are organized in alphabetic order by the author's last name. Enjoy!</p> 
