   <hr size="4"> 
   <h3>Random Quotation Generator</h3> 
   <p>Follow this link for <a href="http://math.furman.edu/cgi-bin/randquote.pl">a random quotation </a>from the collection. The randomizer was written by <a href="http://www-stat.wharton.upenn.edu/~siler/homepage.html">Jack Siler</a> at the University of Pennsylvania.<br> </p> 
   <hr size="4"> 
   <h3><a href="http://math.furman.edu/~mwoodard/pat.html">Pat on the back department...</a></h3> 
   <hr size="3"> 
